<item>
            <title>[LUCENE-1246] Missing a null check in BooleanQuery.toString(String)</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LUCENE-1246</link>
                <project id="12310110" key="LUCENE">Lucene - Core</project>
                        <description>&lt;p&gt;Our queryParser/tokenizer in some situations creates null query and was added as a clause to Boolean query.&lt;br/&gt;
When we try to log the query, NPE is thrown from log(booleanQuery).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In BooleanQuery.toString(String), a simple null check is overlooked.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
